author: @mintelladarling
text:
For everyone asking:
The idol dancing with Kai is Jang Kyungho ('01 liner). Main dancer/vocal of TO1. He is also their performance team leader. He's a very talented dancer. Please check him/TO1 out 🙏


TO1 debuted in 2020 as TOO. They changed their name in 2021.
They have 6 title tracks/MVs as of today with one special single release. They have a small discography, so very easy to check out!

Title tracks/MVs:
- Magnolia
- Count 1, 2
- Son of Beast (my favorite)
- No More X
- Drummin' (what made me a TOgether & my 2nd fave)
- Freeze Tag
- Hug {special single - a remake of TVXQ's song}
